    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[记住：骗我感情可以，骗钱一分没有]]></title>
        <id>2650329055_1</id>
        <link href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4NDEzNTMyMA==&amp;mid=2650329055&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=5d11df0457e1a900b744fbbaebf30eed&amp;chksm=87e7b328b0903a3eaacc7ac9c707dea6508bd8d2e19a9213717141608589e72db7a3f72cc608#rd"/>
        <updated>2024-05-04T15:16:41.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<div style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);visibility: visible;"><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="502845403" data-ratio="0.5731481481481482" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/EC7unEiaL8xrMAa3iav74XfN1ibDpvsFDQzqU9RyjdEzibAN4WAGu25gqtoR97Q4aRyZNEWxzxzHnwLe62kaDqV7fA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p></span></div><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);visibility: visible;"><p><span style="color: rgb(255, 76, 65);"><strong><br></strong></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(255, 76, 65);"><strong>文/六神磊磊</strong></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(255, 76, 65);"><strong><br></strong></span></p><p>胖猫轻生的那个地方，在重庆长江大桥。那个地方我经常开车路过，非常熟悉。</p><p><br></p><p>想不到从今而后，那里会变这个城市一抹悲伤的记忆。</p><p><br></p><p>今天放弃一点政治正确，这个时候搞政治正确很没有意义。关于两性关系那些事，钱也好，性也好，要摊开来说。不然真的有人很糊涂。</p><p><br></p><p>先说说钱。钱面对不同的东西，购买力是不同的。钱在买米买盐的时候你会发现非常值钱。听说有些人前些年买了盐，到现在没吃完。</p><p><br></p><p>钱在买爱的时候，购买力是非常低的。不是不能买，是购买力非常低，往往十块钱只能当一块用。</p><p><br></p><p>尤其是本身就缺钱又缺爱的人，想用钱去买爱，那钱的购买力会低得惊人。</p><p><span style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;"><br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;">尤其你碰上一个根本就不想发货的卖家。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>再说说恋爱关系这件事。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>胖猫和她“在一起”两年，女生也叫他老公。胖猫前前后后给她转了五十多万块钱。问题是只见了两面，吃了一次饭。当然，这是单方面说法，但无疑是屈指可数的。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>人不能见，钱却照收。这说明什么呢？</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>委婉点讲，说明胖猫离这个女生真正的择偶标准差得非常远，不是一点远，是非常。这个差距，胖猫这种老实人再补仓也是不行的。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>口头上的老公，是她最大的极限。这个老公的意思就相当于客户。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>当这种老公，比当路人还惨。如果你正在当这样的老公，那么不妨和对方说一下，改叫客户爸爸好不好。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>同理，如果女生也在当这种老婆的，直接提让男的改叫自己客户爸爸或妈妈。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>希望告诉大家，同样是五十多万，有很多渠道能换来多得多的尊重，哪怕你去买个最糟糕的保单呢，逢年过节还是他问候你，不是你问候他。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>此外有个细节，同样是谈恋爱用钱，两个人消费花了钱，和直接转钱，还是非常不一样的。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>如果五十多万是吃吃喝喝、高餐标、高档消费花掉的，那它可能是一个双方消费标准、消费观不一致的问题。结论可能是：你俩不合适。你伺候不起。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>但频繁直接转钱，多半不是什么消费观的问题，而是杀猪盘的问题。结论可能是：人家把你当猪。</p><p><span style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;"><br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;">那也绝对不要梭哈。老话说，以势交者，势倾则绝。以利交者，利穷则散。把钱留着，至少还会继续叫老公，一把梭哈，那就真被掀桌了。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>还有很多年轻人困惑：如何判断一个人不爱你？</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>基本上是你努力很久，但还是觉得她不爱你，那请相信自己，你是对的。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>这种判断会有偏差，但不会偏差太大。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>关于性的问题，这也很重要。报道里都不太好明确地提性的问题，但也影影绰绰涉及了。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>能看出来，女生明显不愿意和胖猫亲密接触。这说明她身体排斥你。像这种，你再努力，最后也只能换一个东食西宿。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>事实上，哪怕她有意“维护”一下关系，她的心都未必能控制她的身体，因为知易行难。这不是孔融让梨那么简单。对女生来说，排斥就是排斥。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>小师妹被令狐冲不慎扯破袖子，勃然大怒，怒得比任何一次都厉害。小师妹就是忽然意识到，原来自己身体上排斥大师兄。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>这其实是大师兄真正的绝望时刻。可叹大师兄还不明白。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>还有，不要用乞求的方式获得爱情。游坦之把眼睛都给了阿紫，最后又怎么样。</p><p><span style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;"><br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;">对方几乎已经连一点情绪价值都不耐烦给了。比如我想你之类都不耐烦说了。好比聊得越熟悉的技师服务越差。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>乞求，会让自己分外没有魅力。你在别的地方找不到配偶，就拼命乞求我，这是很糟的。人有一种贱性，追涨杀跌，越不缺爱的人越有人爱。不信去动物园看看。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>杨康如果是乞求，你瞧穆念慈还喜不喜欢他。记住，余秀华那句诗，是穿越大半个中国来睡你，而不是穿越大半个中国来求你。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>不管男性还是女性，基本都更喜欢对方明明那么多人中意，却偏喜欢我，而绝不是他没别人要了，所以死缠我。你没人要你也别显出来。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>再不信，去女频看小说，有几部是一个男的实在没别人要，却拼命死缠我的。男频亦然。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>说句难听的，这五十多万，直接扔过去说小姐姐你随便花，无所谓我不要回报，说不定在对方那种人眼里还更有魅力些。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>你一加上乞求，币值立刻贬损，五十万的魅力会贬值得大概只有五万。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>很多时候，明知道对方不爱了，嘴巴上认了，心里却还不认，还想最后做一点什么来挽回，至少是让对方永远铭记自己。比如胖猫最后那让人辛酸的六万多，还加上一句备注自愿赠送，外带订个七百多的花。这是没有效果的。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>更绝对、绝对不要试图用轻生的方式让对方记住你。那是一厢情愿的幻想。你轻生的时刻，搞不好是对方最蔑视你的时刻。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>比我早一辈的文艺青年，都流行读舒婷那一首《致橡树》：</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>“作为树的形象和你站在一起”。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>爱情是种树式的，不是采矿式的。爱情是我在我的土地上种下一颗树，请你来分享我的绿荫。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>而不是往自己心里狠命挖，最后矿石你拿走，黑洞留给我。这个世界上没有人真正爱矿洞，大家爱的都是矿石。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>爱别人的前提一定是爱自己。学会爱自己才有能力爱别人。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>可叹的是我们经常从小就不教大家爱自己，你的使命是付出，你的荣誉是奉献，你的加班是福报，偏偏不是爱自己。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>爱自己不是让你自私，而是要有底线，那就是不能牺牲自尊和健康。事实上，一个人越自尊、越健康，就越有人爱。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>作为年轻人，实在要被骗几回也不是不行，但记住一点：</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>骗我的感情可以，骗我的钱没门。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p>-完-</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="502845404" data-ratio="0.600925925925926" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/EC7unEiaL8xrMAa3iav74XfN1ibDpvsFDQzwkt8mOd7m2wJB9VymUU9FagJgR514Dico8v7X0agfsQfATFCQ45q4TQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">往期推荐：</span><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4NDEzNTMyMA==&amp;mid=2650321708&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b4a5a369c2ba0dbd4d545c93d95dd0b0&amp;chksm=87e7cfdbb09046cddd7c87e24d62ca9ef2dce6dea461aba3b736518319633a597a7756d78c70&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="小师妹：一只胳膊的拒绝" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" style="font-size: 14px;" data-linktype="2"><span style="font-size: 14px;">小师妹：一只胳膊的拒绝</span></a></p></span></div><p style="margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="184" data-backw="464" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="502845396" data-ratio="0.3972222222222222" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;width: 581px !important;visibility: visible !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/EC7unEiaL8xp6CNF9YL3F2V6ZcILKGg3ZB1bXLdJbWpaVbnSmxP